Ya.

114
00:10:13,030 --> 00:10:14,499
Habislah kita.

115
00:10:15,629 --> 00:10:18,629
Jaksa itu akan sadar dan menggunakan media.

116
00:10:19,129 --> 00:10:21,099
Bagaimana cara kita menghadapi semua reporter itu?

117
00:10:26,969 --> 00:10:30,579
Apakah kamu membunuh Oh Il Seung yang asli?

118
00:10:35,950 --> 00:10:37,079
Jadi,

119
00:10:38,619 --> 00:10:40,190
